title: Alus - Alustrious  mixtape
description:
Twenty-year-old sensation Alus has been cementing her way into stardom. Her eight track EP Alustrious showcases her sultry voice and is the beginning to an illustrious journey through her music. The songstress and musician says of Alustrious, "It's a lot of relatable music for everyone. I'm writing what I feel so some of it is fun, sexy, and just feel good music." Follow Alus on Twitter/Instagram @AlusOfficial
